	<article class="post-628113 post type-post status-publish hentry category-mergers-acquisitions category-retailleisure tag-ardian tag-bonomi-andrea-c tag-club-mediterranee-sa tag-fosun-international tag-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures per-bonomi-andrea-c des-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures org-ardian org-club-mediterranee-sa org-fosun-international news_keywords-andrea-c-bonomi news_keywords-ardian news_keywords-club-mediterranee news_keywords-fosun-international news_keywords-mergers-and-acquistions" id="post-628113">
